596
00:28:11,710 --> 00:28:14,470
She can entertain you.

597
00:29:33,470 --> 00:29:34,310
Are you

598
00:29:34,470 --> 00:29:35,990
Zhou Chixiong?

599
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:40,750
Yes.

600
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:27,790
So you're Zhou Chixiong.

601
00:30:29,710 --> 00:30:30,550
