683
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:39,550
A loong!

684
00:35:39,670 --> 00:35:40,990
It'll make you look stronger.

685
00:35:40,990 --> 00:35:42,030
You'll be

686
00:35:42,030 --> 00:35:43,800
